            <p>
              Compute <m>\mu_X</m> and <m>\mu_Y</m> for any two random variables <m>X</m> and <m>Y</m> with joint probabilty distribution function <m>f</m>. 
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </statement>
